document_notes.text:
This update for gawk fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-4156: Fix a heap out of bound read by validating the index into argument list. (bsc#1214025)

notes.text: A heap out-of-bounds read flaw was found in builtin.c in the gawk package. This issue may lead to a crash and could be used to read sensitive information.
